| MakeRiscPkg.oby - Fireworkz-Examples

IfThere $.Temp Then Else %CDir $.Temp

| Remember to update RiscPkg.Control too
Set t5$Release 20151007

Set t5$Disc $.Temp.FzExamples_<t5$Release>
Set t5$Zip  $.Temp.FzExamples_<t5$Release>/zip

X %Wipe <t5$Disc> ~cfr~v

svn export <Obey$Dir> <t5$Disc>

| Remove the examples which only work in Fireworkz Pro
%Wipe   <t5$Disc>.Apps.Document.FzExamples.Mountains ~cfr~v
%Wipe   <t5$Disc>.Apps.Document.FzExamples.Pupils ~cfr~v
%delete <t5$Disc>.Apps.Document.FzExamples.Tutorial.names
%delete <t5$Disc>.Apps.Document.FzExamples.Tutorial.names_b

delete <t5$Disc>._make_w32/cmd

| The one in RiscPkg is the useful one for the packaged examples
delete <t5$Disc>.LICENSE
delete <t5$Disc>.MakeRiscPkg

%Dir <t5$Disc>
zip -r <t5$Zip> RiscPkg Apps
%Back
Info <t5$Zip>

Filer_OpenDir <t5$Disc>
